00:05:43.524 --> 00:05:48.524
and sharing their experiences, you are looking for examples of their attitude.

114
00:05:48.524 --> 00:05:51.524
Things like their viewpoints, their outlook,

115
00:05:51.524 --> 00:05:54.774
their perspectives, maybe a standpoint, position,

